🚀 Part 1: Basic List Operations
📝 Task 1.1: Create and Manipulate Lists

Create an empty list and print it.
Create a list with five integers and print it.
Create a mixed list with at least three different data types and print it.
Code Template:

# Create lists
empty_list = []
