print("Mixed list:", mixed_list)


📝 Task 1.2: Add and Remove Elements
Add an element to the end of the list using append.
Add multiple elements using extend.
Insert an element at a specific position using insert.
Remove a specific element using remove.
Remove and return the last element using pop.
Clear all elements from the list using clear.
Code Template:

# Add elements
my_list = [1, 2, 3]
my_list.append(4)
print("After append:", my_list)

my_list.extend([5, 6])
print("After extend:", my_list)

my_list.insert(2, "new")
print("After insert:", my_list)

# Remove elements
my_list.remove(3)
print("After remove:", my_list)

last_element = my_list.pop()
print("Popped element:", last_element)

my_list.clear()
print("After clear:", my_list)

