🚀 Part 4: Comparisons and Optimization
📝 Task 4.1: Compare Lists and Tuples
Measure performance differences in creation and iteration between lists and tuples.
Code Template:

python
Kopiera kod
import time

# List
start = time.time()
large_list = [x for x in range(1000000)]
print("List created in:", time.time() - start, "seconds")

# Tuple
start = time.time()
large_tuple = tuple(x for x in range(1000000))
print("Tuple created in:", time.time() - start, "seconds")
